OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FScattered to
OL,6,Ffrequent blustery showers feed in from
OL,7,Fthe west through the evening and
OL,8,Fovernight, these showers heavy at
OL,9,Ftimes. Staying driest in eastern
OL,10,FBorders.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FIt will be quite cool with
OL,13,Fbright or sunny spells and scattered
OL,14,Fheavy showers. Blustery winds around
OL,15,Fthe southwest coast. Chance of
OL,16,Fovernight frost in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
