OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FRather cold Thursday with scattered
OL,7,Fheavy showers, chance of overnight
OL,8,Ffrost. Some early showers on Friday,
OL,9,Fotherwise dry with sunny spells.
OL,10,FMostly dry and bright Saturday, rain
OL,11,Fin west later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
